# Setup guide
https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/setup.html

# Free Cloud Trial:
https://www.elastic.co/cloud/cloud-trial-overview/30-days?ultron=community-beginners-crash-course-May2022+&hulk=30d 


# Windows Installation: 
https://dev.to/elastic/downloading-elasticsearch-and-kibana-macos-linux-and-windows-1mmo 


https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/zip-windows.html 



# Installation on Linux and Mac:
https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/targz.html  


# Alternative installation using Docker:
Refer "docker-compose.yml" file

docker-compose up -d

--------------------------

# Change config

config/elasticsearch.yml 

---------------------
# Start Elasticsearch / Kibana

bin/elasticsearch (or on windows: bin/elasticsearch.bat)

bin/kibana (or on windows: bin/kibana.bat)

--------------------------------------
# After successful launch access elasticsearch and kibana

# Elasticsearch
curl http://loclahost:9200
or
from browser search for  http://loclahost:9200

# Kibana
curl http://loclahost:5601
or
from browser search for  http://loclahost:5601
---------------------------------------------


